    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This specimen is powered by the S54 3.2L high-revving inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls flawlessly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a Variable M Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. This vehicle has undergone proactive maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension kinematics remain sharp with OEM bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the cross-drilled rotors and multi-piston calipers offer fade-free deceleration. No pixel degradation in the cluster and zero interior bolster wear\u2014this is a true collector-tier enthusiast vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
