    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands in 'as-new' condition, perfect for the most discerning collector or enthusiast. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen a day of inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like luster with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, further protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a masterclass in preservation; the leather seats remain firm and supple with no creasing or wear on the bolsters, and the original factory protective films are still present on several trim pieces. Every button, switch, and digital interface operates with the precision of the day it was manufactured. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative, featuring a comprehensive service history exclusively through authorized technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is spotless, showing no signs of road use. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality example that looks, smells, and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line. All original keys, manuals, and service records are included.",
